## Task: Collaborative Red Teaming MVP — runnable demo slice (in-process, no crypto/TEE)

**Goal.** Build the smallest *working code* slice of CRT that demonstrates the differentiator —
**coverage is shared, attribution is private** — end to end, from a CLI, with no ClickHouse, MPC,
TEE, ZK, or real federation. This is the technical companion to `crt_showcase_demo.html`. It must
slot under the SAME interfaces as the full A.5 build so the heavy crypto can be added later without
re-architecture.

